{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_13_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "んしょ……。ふぅ、寮まで後少しなのに\nやっぱり物が多いと大変ですね",
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7795007388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ララさん達がやって来てから、結構経ったもんな\nその月日の分だけ、事務所にも物が増えたんだろう",
      "startTime": 13.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "多過ぎますけどね。寮にも一杯あるんですよ\nでも、ちょっとほしいと思う物もあります",
      "startTime": 22.8904992421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6848297437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "触るとあっという間に着替えられる発明品とか\n衣装替えの時間を大幅に縮められますし",
      "startTime": 30.5238325755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.9780721665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、それは確かに使えそうだな\n星見プロの人数分を頼んだら引き受けてくれるかな？",
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、別の星の技術ですし、使うにしても\nララさん達がいる間だけの方がいいのかも……",
      "startTime": 46.9068220686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.5442168236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、その……つ、使おうとしたら……\nまた変なトラブルが起きてしまうかもしれませんし",
      "startTime": 56.2487533569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5475478809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、着替えるつもりが別の衣装になったりとかな\nそういえば俺も、こころのイタズラで水着にされたよ",
      "startTime": 65.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2039006235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　きゅ、急に水着とか……っ……\nも、もうこの話はやめましょう！　思わず想像を……",
      "startTime": 74.3989363988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.5172351203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな。想像するだけでも恥ずかしいよな\n余計なことを言ってすまなかった",
      "startTime": 83.7333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、衣装を一瞬で変えて、ヤミさんみたいに髪の毛の\n長さを変えたり出来たら……夢がありますよね",
      "startTime": 90.4628164928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0206145607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "曲ごとに髪型を変えられたら、表現の幅も広がりますし\nちなみにヤミさんは、髪の毛以外も変えられるそうです",
      "startTime": 100.3638239354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "でもあれは、ヤミさん自身の能力なので\n私達には真似出来ないみたいで。残念ですけど",
      "startTime": 108.5294831594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3256038669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、本当に残念だな。猫の手も借りたい時があるし\n髪の毛が手になったら、便利そうだと思ったんだが",
      "startTime": 119.0666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それに格好いいよな。もし何かあったら\n俺がその力で、みんなを守れるし。……なんてな",
      "startTime": 127.2333374024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0279619538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……っぷ、あははっ\n{user}さんにそんな一面があったなんて",
      "startTime": 134.2328424454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、そんなこと、めったに起きませんよ\nそれに、今も十分守ってもらってます",
      "startTime": 141.5994913101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.7854753498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "た、たまに考えないか？　もし悪いやつが乗り込んで\n来たら、とか……いや、やっぱり忘れてくれ",
      "startTime": 150.2036937886,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14516.630409800002,
          "startTime": 164.7203241984
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17109.95001020001,
          "startTime": 167.3136437988
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.0057928725
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.686974589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、忘れることは出来ませんけど、秘密にします\nさて、そろそろ行きましょうか。んしょ……とと……",
      "startTime": 161.686974589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.1302824024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ふらついてるけど大丈夫か？　疲れが残ってるなら……\nって、あれ？　この発明品、箱の蓋が……開いてる？",
      "startTime": 172.9333374024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.0423005744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、よろけた拍子にタッチパネルに\n触れちゃったみたいで……ど、どうしよう……！",
      "startTime": 183.5994921366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　でもこの大きな箱……良かった、大丈夫です\nこの大きな箱は、冷凍庫みたいなものだって聞きました",
      "startTime": 195.6353232431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.1721633916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "空間歪曲システム？　で食材を沢山保存出来るそうで\nララさんがお料理の時に使っていました",
      "startTime": 206.5994911193,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7500.508880699982,
          "startTime": 214.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8367.175547399995,
          "startTime": 214.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10333.842213999986,
          "startTime": 216.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11200.5088807,
          "startTime": 217.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 215.5333374024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ただの冷凍庫か。なら安心だな。てっきりまた妙な……\nうわぁ！？　何か出てきているぞ！　タ、タコ！？",
      "startTime": 215.5333374024,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13033.333333299994,
          "startTime": 228.5666707357
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13033.333333299994,
          "startTime": 228.5666707357
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "これも食材なのか！？　というか大き過ぎるぞ！\n瑠依、ここは俺に任せてララさん達を――うわぁ！？",
      "startTime": 225.6666707357,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5051.150957600015,
          "startTime": 230.7178216933
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5051.150957600015,
          "startTime": 230.7178216933
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6617.817624300016,
          "startTime": 232.28448836
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6617.817624300016,
          "startTime": 232.28448836
        }
      ]
    },
